        },
        "subject": "LU-16035 kfilnd: Fix immediate buffer ref count",
        "message": "LU-16035 kfilnd: Fix immediate buffer ref count\n\nThe current implementation has a race condition where two threads\ncould repost the same immediate buffer. To resolve this issue,\nthe ref count value is now checked atomically when decremented. Once\nthe ref count is zero, the immediate buffer will be reposted.\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial\nHPE-bug-id: LUS-9348\nSigned-off-by: Ian Ziemba <ian.ziemba@hpe.com>\nChange-Id: I1c6d2f9ba9009ce2c21de189f8f4760cc59f05df\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
  },
